{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Keyword list to choose from is now grouped by category\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Added {\f1 CENTALT}, and {\f1 CENTAZ} keywords\par}
