{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The camera temperature setpoint is now displayed {\i only} when the cooler is active\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab A secondary HIPS2 server will be attempted if the main HIPS2 image server is not available\par}
