{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Fixed a bug in Autofocus routine that could wrongly declare an autofocus run a failure if the starting point couldn\u8217't detect any stars\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Fixed custom color schema not saving properly and resetting to default when reloading the application\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The backlash measurement routine has been fixed so that the focuser is properly recentered before the backlashOUT measurement procedure\par}
