{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab When EOS Utility is running in the background, the x64 N.I.N.A. client will scan for this app and prevent a crash due to the EOS utility being open. Instead a notification will show up to close the EOS Utility.\par}
