{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Image HFR is now available as an image file name token ({\f1 $$HFR$$})\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Focuser Temperature is now available as an image file name token ({\f1 $$FOCUSERTEMP$$})\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Added a clear button on HFR History graph. The button will be displayed when hovering the control.\par}
